    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
          <h1 class="blue-title">What we do.</h1>
          <p>Here at puntsquad we provide +EV tips on sports that are guaranteed to turn you a profit in the long run. We want you to learn to be a smarter and more objective punter by learning the statistical outlook. We've even prepared a comprehensive guide to get you started.<p>

          <%= link_to "Learn More", bettingguide_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag("daily-tip.png", size: '100') %>
          <h3 class="blue-title">Tips Daily</h3>
          <p>Tips are published daily straight to our Website by our professional tippers. As a bonus, these tips are also emailed straight to your inbox for a more on-the-go option.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag("stats.png", size: '100')%>
          <h3 class="blue-title">Result Analysis</h3>
          <p>Sportsbetting is a process that requires patience and dedication. Although we guarantee a profit in the long run, we do sometimes lose. Therefore we provide detailed weekly analysis and statistics on all of our bets so that our customers can better understand the process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag("basketball.png", size: '100')%>
          <h3 class="blue-title">All Sports</h3>
          <p>Unlike other tipping sites out there, we charge a single subscription fee that encompasses all the sports which we tip on. No longer will you have to pay for multiple subscriptions for different sports.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

